{"tid":356431,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"暑假幾時先完呀屌你老母","createTime":"2017-08-12T05:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T10:47:24.000Z","uid":12618,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35d1878d5437055b0250ef6283b1ba3ce543fad7","tid":356431,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"每一日一街都係小朋友<br />\n上親邊架車/去親邊度食野都一定有小朋友叫喊聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因不外乎扭計要玩具同開心會尖叫<br />\n佢仆街老豆老母又唔撚理<br />\n仲有果堆爺爺嫲嫲 <br />\n只會覺得小朋友活潑 小朋友就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識生唔識教<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有時真係好想一野大大拍落佢老母個臭閪度大叫識扑野又唔識教仔</span><br />\n<br />\n而家天氣熱<br />\n有啲小朋友誇張到除鞋  <br />\n拿起條裙抖涼 成條底褲露撚晒出黎<br />\n仆街 被逼睇cp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚煩呀屌你老母  <br />\n屌又屌過 可以行開都盡量避<br />\n好撚想暑假快撚啲完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75222715b94f33af320de4b9aedfaf8f7b17c73","tid":356431,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n拿起條裙抖涼 成條底褲露撚晒出黎<br />\n仆街 被逼睇cp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真！"},{"pid":"7d0835f1a21643b3858ff8bc3f32f889ce5edd87","tid":356431,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"但我法國暑假都多左好多短褲背心"},{"pid":"9d2e89ebeaa7b19afd8d4b31f788a549d71686d8","tid":356431,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n拿起條裙抖涼 成條底褲露撚晒出黎<br />\n仆街 被逼睇cp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<i